.TH DADNS 1 "2026-01-02" "dumbass-tree" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
dadns \- DNS sanity helper (systemd-resolved / resolv.conf / NetworkManager)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B dadns
[--dry-run] [-v] <command>
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B status
Show resolv.conf mode, service status, and (if available) resolvectl output.
.TP
.B set-mode stub|real|static
Switch /etc/resolv.conf wiring with safety prompts.
.TP
.B stub-listener --on|--off
Enable/disable systemd-resolved's 127.0.0.53 stub listener.
.TP
.B nm-dns systemd-resolved|default|none
Set NetworkManager DNS plugin mode via a drop-in.
.TP
.B flush
Flush systemd-resolved caches (resolvectl flush-caches).
